   AMERICAN CAPITAL &amp; RESEARCH Corp. (Fairfax, Va.) -- Samuel
Belzberg, 61-year-old chairman and chief executive officer of
First City Financial Corp., was named a director of this
environmental services company, as part of a board
restructuring in which eight management directors stepped
down, reducing board membership to nine. Mr. Belzberg and his
family own about 12.2% of American Capital's Class A common
stock through an affiliate.
